Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.46,0:02:40.17,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,All pirates who seek One Piece strive to reach the second half of the Grand Line...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.17,0:02:42.67,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,The place called the New World.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.13,0:02:51.43,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,However, the only one who ever conquered that ocean was the Pirate King, Gold Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.52,0:02:57.65,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,The New World has killed the dreams and ambitions of countless pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.55,0:03:04.11,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,And now, the boy who ate the \NGomu Gomu Fruit and became a rubber man,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.11,0:03:07.36,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,Monkey D. Luffy and his crew are going to challenge that sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.15,0:03:11.67,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.36,0:03:17.33,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,Luffy and his friends departed Dress Rosa,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.80,0:03:23.50,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,and were en route to their next destination, Zou,\N to meet up with the other half of their crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.50,0:03:26.09,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,Out of the blue, they were attacked by battle boats,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.09,0:03:31.42,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,and Luffy was taken to the mysterious island\NSilver Mine, along with Bartolomeo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.90,0:03:37.85,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,His life threatened by the leader of the Silver Pirate Alliance, Bill,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.35,0:03:43.73,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,Luffy falls into an underground mine shaft,\N where he learns the truth about Bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.73,0:03:48.24,Main,Desire,0,0,0,,Lies!  There ain't no way Bill would do that to his own crew! {ep748 copypaste start}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.24,0:03:50.45,Main,Silver Slave Miner,0,0,0,,I know it's hard to believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.45,0:03:52.45,Main,Silver Slave Miner,0,0,0,,But it's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.66,0:03:57.54,Main,Desire,0,0,0,,Hey!  Did Bill really tell you to...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.25,0:04:00.75,Main,Desire,0,0,0,,get rid of {\i1}me{\i0} as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.75,0:04:01.92,Main,Avelon,0,0,0,,Indeed he did!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.30,0:04:05.51,Main,Desire,0,0,0,,So that's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.57,0:04:09.37,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Gomu Gomu no...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.58,0:04:15.18,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,...Jet Bazooka!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.90,0:04:29.99,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,I fought side-by-side with Luffy-senpai fer the first time!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.62,0:04:39.96,Main,Peseta,0,0,0,,If Straw Hat and the others\N make it up here, we'll be in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.75,0:04:50.13,Main,Bill,0,0,0,,Then, let's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.13,0:04:51.51,Main,Bill,0,0,0,,bury them all. {ep748 copypaste end}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.09,0:05:06.61,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,This the right track?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.61,0:05:09.65,Main,Silver Slave Miner,0,0,0,,Yeah, that one goes all the way to the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.65,0:05:11.70,Main,Silver Slave Miner,0,0,0,,They were using it to carry ore out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.13,0:05:15.41,Main,Silver Slave Miner,0,0,0,,But we dunno what lies ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.81,0:05:19.75,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,So's we gotta leave it up ta luck,\Nright, Luffy-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.28,0:05:23.75,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Alright, we're off!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.75,0:05:26.17,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.17,0:05:29.55,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm {\i1}so{\i0} thrilled!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.55,0:05:37.09,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,I'm answerin' Luffy-senpai's commands, \Nalmost like I'm one o' the Straw Hats!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.59,0:05:43.48,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,What's this?  You guys sure ain't very lively.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.48,0:05:45.86,Main,Silver Slave Miner,0,0,0,,Well, we {\i1}do{\i0} wanna get out of here, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.86,0:05:49.48,Main,Silver Slave Miner,0,0,0,,If Bill finds us, we'll just end up back here again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.48,0:05:52.36,Main,Silver Slave Miner,0,0,0,,On top of that, we'll be on the receiving end of harsh punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.36,0:05:54.78,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,What're y'all afraid of?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.78,0:05:56.74,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,Luffy-senpai's strong as a hundred men!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.74,0:05:59.08,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,Wait, no, a thousand!  Ten thousand!  {\i1}A hundred million!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.08,0:06:00.12,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,No, no, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.12,0:06:01.87,Main,Desire,0,0,0,,Give it a rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.87,0:06:06.79,Main,Silver Slave Miner,0,0,0,,Even so, it don't matter how strong he is,\Nhe's no match for Bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.79,0:06:11.26,Main,Silver Slave Miner,0,0,0,,I don't wanna have molten metal\N poured on me and be turned into a statue!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.59,0:06:16.09,Main,Silver Slave Miner,0,0,0,,And it's not just Bill.  They've got this scary commander named Peseta too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.09,0:06:19.31,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,Feh!  Do whatever ya want, fer all I care!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.31,0:06:20.37,Main,Desire,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.17,0:06:25.35,Main,Desire,0,0,0,,I've made up my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.35,0:06:28.82,Main,Desire,0,0,0,,I'm gettin' outta here with \NStraw Hat an' settlin' things!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.82,0:06:30.32,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,"Settlin' things"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.96,0:06:33.95,Main,Desire,0,0,0,,So y'all wanna spend the rest of your lives here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.95,0:06:37.87,Main,Desire,0,0,0,,If you stay here, yer jus' waitin' ta be murdered!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.87,0:06:43.16,Main,Desire,0,0,0,,An' if that's the case, ain't ya better off\N takin' your chances tryin' ta get off this island?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.64,0:06:45.79,Main,Desire,0,0,0,,Have some guts!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.22,0:06:48.37,Main,Desire,0,0,0,,That is, if ya call yerself a pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.34,0:06:53.38,Main,Silver Slave Miner,0,0,0,,I'm going!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.38,0:06:54.26,Main,Silver Slave Miner,0,0,0,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.26,0:06:56.93,Main,Desire,0,0,0,,Huh?  I can't hear ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.47,0:07:03.56,Main,Silver Slave Miners,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're goin' along with him!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.38,0:07:06.81,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Right, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.81,0:07:09.90,Main,Silver Slave Miners,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yeah!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.53,0:07:15.65,Main,Peseta,0,0,0,,Good job getting here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.17,0:07:34.26,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,Luffy-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.69,0:07:40.55,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Gomu Gomu no...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.55,0:07:42.74,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Balloon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.52,0:07:59.61,Thoughts,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,I'm landing on Luffy-senpai's Gomu Gomu Balloon! {one of those moments where I hate that we're still using "Gomu Gomu no" -Jules}{There's something oddly sexual about this... It makes me uncomfortable @_@}{If only it was Robin's bosom instead...}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.61,0:08:02.25,Thoughts,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,Such bliss!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.87,0:08:07.08,Main,Desire,0,0,0,,Don't fall asleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.47,0:08:10.79,Main,Silver Slave Miner,0,0,0,,Watch out!  The overpass is collapsing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.91,0:08:20.09,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,Lemme handle this!  Barrier!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.96,0:08:29.64,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Nice job, Hen-comb!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.64,0:08:34.40,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,Thanks!  I'm honored ta be of service!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.00,0:08:41.57,Main,Peseta,0,0,0,,This is really...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.43,0:08:47.62,Main,Peseta,0,0,0,,{\i1}Really{\i0} incredible, incredible, incredible!{Does this guy think he's part of the Ginyu force? -Fadeout4}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.62,0:08:51.12,Main,Desire,0,0,0,,Peseta!  Are these part o' Bill's orders, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.12,0:08:53.25,Main,Peseta,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.25,0:08:57.90,Main,Desire,0,0,0,,And yer gonna bury these guys alive as well, \Nafter driving them so hard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.21,0:09:01.76,Main,Peseta,0,0,0,,Trying to spare just them would be... {Not sure if the first "just" should be removed, or if it's supposed to be something like "Trying to spare just them", as in sparing the slaves and not Luffy, Desire, etc. Needs TLC.}{Indeed it is as in "Sparing the slaves, killing Luffy and his merry band of companions". -Starfish}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.76,0:09:06.35,Main,Peseta,0,0,0,,an {\i1}incredible{\i0} pain in the rear!  So I'll just be...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.84,0:09:09.35,Main,Peseta,0,0,0,,taking care of them along with you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.35,0:09:11.23,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,Now I'm pissed!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.23,0:09:13.31,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,Barrier Crush!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.15,0:09:25.78,Main,Peseta,0,0,0,,Your barrier's as dangerous as they say.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.33,0:09:28.66,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,It ain't {\i1}just{\i0} "dangerous"!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.66,0:09:30.87,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,Bari-ability!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.87,0:09:32.29,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,Stairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.10,0:09:51.98,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Oh, the barrier stairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.98,0:09:54.65,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,Climb 'em, Luffy-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.65,0:09:56.56,Main,Desire,0,0,0,,Why're you lookin' the other way?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.56,0:09:59.53,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Alright!  Hen-comb, I'm goin' on ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.53,0:10:01.24,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,Please take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.24,0:10:03.81,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,Oh, I mean, I'm comin' with!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.76,0:10:09.54,Thoughts,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,This is awesome!  I'm havin' {\i1}so{\i0} much fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.12,0:10:16.45,Main,Peseta,0,0,0,,If I'm correct, there's a limit to the size of the barrier you can produce at one time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.89,0:10:27.19,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,Why ya dirty...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.68,0:10:32.68,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,I used it all up on the staircase!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.44,0:10:42.28,Main,Desire,0,0,0,,Follow Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.60,0:10:44.40,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,Climb up as fast as ya can!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.40,0:10:47.16,Main,Silver Slave Miners,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yeah!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.12,0:10:51.79,Main,Silver Brother,0,0,0,,Peseta-sama!  We must do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.79,0:10:55.62,Main,Peseta,0,0,0,,Don't panic!\NI already have Plans B and C ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.91,0:11:13.35,Main,Silver Brother,0,0,0,,We're gonna burn you all to a crisp!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.52,0:11:25.57,Main,Law,0,0,0,,Shambles!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.11,0:11:29.53,Main,Kin'emon,0,0,0,,Pardon!  Foxfire Style...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.39,0:11:32.74,Main,Kin'emon,0,0,0,,Fire-Willow Flash!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.12,0:11:36.25,Main,Silver Brother,0,0,0,,What the?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.75,0:11:37.91,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Kin'emon!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.67,0:11:43.80,Main,Kin'emon,0,0,0,,There is no fire that I cannot cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.50,0:11:53.78,Main,Law,0,0,0,,You deal with the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.77,0:12:04.86,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Gomu Gomu no...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.86,0:12:07.60,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Elephant Gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.11,0:12:21.25,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,We're finally outta there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.14,0:12:28.55,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,Luffy-senpai's Elephant Gun!\N I got ta see somethin' awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.55,0:12:31.05,Main,Desire,0,0,0,,What're ya standin' there for?\NLet's go already!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.52,0:12:36.43,Main,Peseta,0,0,0,,Ah ah, you're not going any further!\NDon't think you've won just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.37,0:12:38.94,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,You again, Penta?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.94,0:12:41.40,Main,Peseta,0,0,0,,It's {\i1}Peseta!{\i0}  Get a load of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.92,0:12:45.86,Main,Desire,0,0,0,,The gals!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.38,0:12:48.40,Main,Silver Sister,0,0,0,,Desire!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.40,0:12:51.36,Main,Peseta,0,0,0,,If you resist, I'll put an end to their lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.36,0:12:54.08,Main,Peseta,0,0,0,,So, you gonna come along quietly?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.79,0:12:57.04,Main,Kin'emon,0,0,0,,Most unfair!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.04,0:13:00.79,Main,Desire,0,0,0,,Peseta, yer lower than low!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.00,0:13:06.39,Main,Peseta,0,0,0,,"Lower than low"?  You've got it all wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.01,0:13:10.93,Main,Peseta,0,0,0,,You mean "incredible", don't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.30,0:13:21.31,Main,Desire,0,0,0,,You gals okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.85,0:13:23.15,Main,Silver Sisters,0,0,0,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.04,0:13:26.90,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.27,0:14:08.23,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.23,0:14:10.53,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,When his friends have their backs to th' wall,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.53,0:14:13.07,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,he appears in th' nick o' time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.07,0:14:15.91,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's Zoro-senpai!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.43,0:14:20.62,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,Luffy, I owe him a debt of pain.  Let me handle this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.20,0:14:22.79,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,That so?  'Kay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.25,0:14:29.34,Main,Peseta,0,0,0,,You sure seem relaxed,\NPirate Hunter Zoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.34,0:14:32.55,Main,Peseta,0,0,0,,You might have a bounty of 320 million,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.55,0:14:36.16,Main,Peseta,0,0,0,,but you were {\i1}incredibly{\i0} pathetic when we last met!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.50,0:14:41.24,Main,Peseta,0,0,0,,Laugh at him!  Feel free to laugh at him, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.16,0:14:51.07,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,What a jerk!\NHow dare 'e make fun o' Zoro-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.07,0:14:53.50,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,I'ma beat the crap outta of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.66,0:14:56.61,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,Luffy-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.74,0:14:59.99,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,He said {\i1}he'll{\i0} do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.60,0:15:05.04,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,Bring it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.47,0:15:12.13,Main,Peseta,0,0,0,,You don't know your place!\NI'll immobilize you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.52,0:15:29.19,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,Single-Sword Style: Draw...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.07,0:15:39.41,Main,Peseta,0,0,0,,No way!  My Adhesive Shell \Nshould stick to anything that it touches!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.10,0:15:45.75,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,Any swordsman who allows that disgusting crap to touch his blade would shame themselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.08,0:15:48.63,Main,Kin'emon,0,0,0,,Only Zoro-dono is capable of such feats!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.63,0:15:50.13,Main,Desire,0,0,0,,What jus' happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.13,0:15:56.17,Main,Bartolomeo,0,0,0,,Zoro-senpai diced up every last Adhesive Shell in a single slash!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.39,0:15:59.39,Main,Peseta,0,0,0,,This is far from over!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.39,0:16:00.43,Main,Peseta,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.26,0:16:02.22,Main,Peseta,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.22,0:16:03.39,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.40,0:16:13.78,Main,Peseta,0,0,0,,Why you... You... You...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.26,0:16:15.85,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,Three-Sword Style...
