Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.96,0:16:38.13,Main,Silver Brother,0,0,0,,This sucks!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.13,0:16:39.91,Main,Silver Brothers,0,0,0,,{\i1}This sucks!{\i0} {i guess we can hear this too}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.20,0:16:43.01,Main,Kin'emon,0,0,0,,Splendid!
