Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.74,0:17:30.27,Main,Silver Sister,0,0,0,,We won't leave until you come back to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.34,0:17:31.90,Main,Desire,0,0,0,,Yeah!
