Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.79,0:20:34.29,Main,Desire,0,0,0,,Straw Hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.68,0:20:37.58,Main,Desire,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the one ta settle the score with 'im.
